(21,$t$1.4B$t$,$r$below_161$r$,$d$easy$d$,$s$What is this coin worth?$s$,$v$<svg viewBox="0 0 260 115" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><rect width="100%" height="115" fill="white"/><image href="/assets/dime.jpg" x="18" y="25" width="64" height="64" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"/></svg>$v$,$e$The coin shown is a dime. A dime is worth 10 cents.$e$,$n$Original Grade 1 math preview seed: TestingMom reference batch 1$n$,$c$[{"label":"A","body":"1 cent","is_correct":false,"sort_order":1,"misconception":"Misread a coin value or money notation.","misconception_tag":"money_value_or_notation"},{"label":"B","body":"5 cents","is_correct":false,"sort_order":2,"misconception":"Misread a coin value or money notation.","misconception_tag":"money_value_or_notation"},{"label":"C","body":"10 cents","is_correct":true,"sort_order":3,"misconception":null,"misconception_tag":null},{"label":"D","body":"25 cents","is_correct":false,"sort_order":4,"misconception":"Misread a coin value or money notation.","misconception_tag":"money_value_or_notation"}]$c$::jsonb),
